OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FTemperatures will feel
OL,6,Fsignificantly cooler than today.
OL,7,FRather cloudy morning with some patchy
OL,8,Frain, mostly confined across Argyll.
OL,9,FMainly dry for the afternoon with
OL,10,Fbrighter spells.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,13,Fearly Thursday, clearing to showers
OL,14,Ffor the afternoon. Friday turning wet
OL,15,Fand windy with best of shelter in
OL,16,Feast. Showers Saturday, more frequent
OL,17,Fin west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
